{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a9b9d824aa","title":"中共中央转发桂北区党委关于县城郊区土改问题的电报","origin":"根据文件的原件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"333afba027","index":0,"year":1951,"month":2,"day":13,"articleId":"a9b9d824aa"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"25bb4291b1","type":"title","text":"中共中央转发桂北区党委关于县城郊区土改问题的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a9b9d824aa"},{"id":"8f6e2f7c3a","type":"appellation","text":"华东局、西北局、西南局：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a9b9d824aa"},{"id":"024f752ddc","type":"paragraph","text":"现将中南局转发桂北区党委一月十五日电发给你们参考。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a9b9d824aa"},{"id":"6b3a0e3fb3","type":"paragraph","text":" 中  央二月十三日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a9b9d824aa"},{"id":"7825b5c040","type":"subtitle","text":"桂北区党委电如下：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a9b9d824aa"},{"id":"dc3eb9a110","type":"paragraph","text":"各县多以县城的郊区作土改试点，原因是：这些郊区靠近县的领导机关，过去较有基础，行动又便于指导，但农民一起来，往往牵涉到工商业，对市民震动颇大，不易掌握。故规定今后每县县城郊区土改必须放到该到土改接近完成时再搞。那时干部对土改更有经验，对于政策与群众情绪的掌握会更稳。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a9b9d824aa"}],"page":{"id":"23977ff8e1","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a9b9d824aa","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}